Sqoyaw（環山部落）

Itiniay i Heping Cen no Taichung ko Sqoyaw a niyaro’, 233  ko sa’osi no parod no loma’, 699 ko sa’osi no tamdaw.

80% ko ka’aloman no Yincomin, polong han i, 557  ko tamdaw; o roma sato i, 20% ko ka’aloman no roma a finacadan, polong han i, 142 ko tamdaw.

O pa-sin-to(百分比) no ka’aloman no tamdaw no kasafinacadan i, ko Tayal73%, Amis1%, Bunun1%, Paiwan1%, roma3%.

Ira ko picodadan(平等國小) i niyaro’.

Ira ko imeng(和平分局環山派出所) i niyaro’.

Ira ko Kiwkay(台灣基督長老教會環山教會、真耶穌教會環山教會、基督復臨安息日會環山教會、環山天主堂) i niyaro’.

